revno: 902 [merge]
committer: Tom Cato Amundsen <tca@gnu.org>
branch nick: solfege.dev
timestamp: Sat 2008-12-13 09:50:28 +0100
message:
  Change the Track api, so that we specify the volume for each track,
  and added default values for velocity so that exercises don't have
  to enter the velocity in most cases. Updated the exercises.
  
  Change the GUI in the preferences for "Use different instrument for
  chords and harmonic intervals" to use the Gtk volume widget.
  
  Added more unit tests testing lesson file music objects to make
  sure the correct midi events are generated.
  
  Changed how some music objects handle config/override_default_instrument,
  since it was pretty random.
