timestamp: Tue 2010-11-23 18:39:35 +0100
message:
  The submenu on the frontpage looked for user generated front page
  files in app_data()/exercises/*/*, but it should be
  user_data()/exercises/*/*.
  I did not notice this on linux since those directories are the same.
  But on windows, app_data() is in C:\Documents and Settings\User\App data,
  and user_data() is a "GNU Solfege" folder in "My documents"
